Marie-Christine Barrault https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie-Christine_Barrault 0 Marie-Christine Barrault (born 21 March 1944) is a French actress. She is best known for her performance in Cousin Cousine (1975) for which she was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Actress. In 2010, she released her autobiography, titled This Long Way To Get To You. Marie-Christine_Barrault ( born 21_March_1944 ) is a_French_actress .
